<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='635932' id='t-635932'>This is a spectacular coral garden.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='638068' id='t-638068'>We didn't even expect
to find things this beautiful.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='640650' id='t-640650'>It's thousands of meters deep.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='642558' id='t-642558'>There are new species.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='644416' id='t-644416'>It's just a beautiful place.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='646339' id='t-646339'>There are fossils in amongst,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='647744' id='t-647744'>and now I've trained you
to appreciate the fossil corals</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='650459' id='t-650459'>that are down there.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:02
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='651698' id='t-651698'>So next time you're lucky enough
to fly over the ocean</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='654588' id='t-654588'>or sail over the ocean,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='656021' id='t-656021'>just think -- there are massive
sea mountains down there</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='658712' id='t-658712'>that nobody's ever seen before,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='660603' id='t-660603'>and there are beautiful corals.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:13
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='662244' id='t-662244'>Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:14
